Package uk.ac.rdg.resc.edal.catalogue

Class DataCatalogue

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.rdg.resc.edal.catalogue.DataCatalogue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CatalogueConfig.DatasetStorage, DatasetCatalogue, FeatureCatalogue
    public class DataCatalogue
extends Object
implements DatasetCatalogue, CatalogueConfig.DatasetStorage, FeatureCatalogue
    A catalogues which implements DatasetCatalogue, CatalogueConfig.DatasetStorage, and FeatureCatalogue. Given a CacheConfiguration, this is able to return Datasets, and Collections of DiscreteFeatures given a single String layer identifier. It also provides a cache of DiscreteFeatures for speed.
    Author:
    Guy Griffiths
